text: The 2017 6 Metre World Cup was held in Vancouver, Canada 17–21 September 2017 hosted by Royal Vancouver Yacht Club. Phillippe Durr won the World Championship title. ==Results== ===Open division=== ===Classic division=== ==References== Category:6 Metre World Cup 6 Metre World Cup Category:Sailing competitions in Canada Category:2017 in Canadian sports
